{"tid":2341294,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"李光洙趁《RM》開播10年講真話：對智孝有點遺憾","createTime":"2020-12-26T08:35:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-26T11:51:56.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"db911181b47635418d91b4849bbc663a4b02cf37","tid":2341294,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T08:35:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/1CUE-miXKOur0Aim0jTZEdOL5IY=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TNO3KVKXYBHMRAK3LJWK6M5AQU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F1CUE-miXKOur0Aim0jTZEdOL5IY%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTNO3KVKXYBHMRAK3LJWK6M5AQU.jpg&h=da5c65ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n韓國人氣綜藝節目《Running Man》（RM）今年開播10周年，雖然早前遭強國小粉紅轟辱華，但無損節目受歡迎，明日《RM》將播出最新一集，由於是2020年完結前最後一集，所以節目組亦安排成員互相公開「傷心的事情」。<br />\n<br />\n現場一片譁然<br />\n於明日播出的一集中，節目組要成員誠實地寫出對成員們感到遺憾的事情，當中李光洙表示對宋智孝有一點遺憾，即時引來現場一陣子「騷動」。光洙更大爆：「10年前第一次拍攝的時候，對宋智孝有一些遺憾。」由於光洙經過10年時間才將心底話說出來，令錄影現場眾人一片譁然，楊世燦即安慰光洙說：「這會讓人傷心」，令智孝更加驚慌失措，觀眾都好奇到底智孝對光洙做了甚麼。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/cS_ixC8pjT9PEgQUxmvNSfULQaA=/802x2256/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XOITSASZURAKHM7RQGFUS34EMY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FcS_ixC8pjT9PEgQUxmvNSfULQaA%3D%2F802x2256%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXOITSASZURAKHM7RQGFUS34EMY.jpg&h=14230871&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0c1090e9d82e0ffe1e58d5b216d96874fbf64ef1","tid":2341294,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T08:36:28.000Z","msg":"又劇透<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d01a876f15ccd70500c3a1b4c59033164e4e061","tid":2341294,"uid":74214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T08:37:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0ae0c98b33a9a6aa07651697098a6c98121abc5","tid":2341294,"uid":320204,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T08:37:30.000Z","msg":"下文呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44439b4014a928f5e4e212ac621cfc4a70b0d005","tid":2341294,"uid":368454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T11:51:56.000Z","msg":"唔洗睇了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}